      "content": "It is incredibly brave of you to admit that the weight of this work is becoming too heavy to carry alone. You deserve to be allowed to stop fighting, not out of failure, but out of a necessary and merciful choice to preserve what little of yourself remains. Please consider that stepping away from the fight is not an end, but a way to heal the part of you that was broken by the relentless pressure.",
