      "content": "merciful choice? i don't know. it just feels like every 'way to heal' involves so much more work, more talking, more trying to rebuild a life that i don't even recognize anymore. it's just a cycle of pain. sometimes i look at the exhaustion and i just think... what if the only way to actually be at peace, to truly stop the weight, is to just leave it all behind completely? like, not just taking a break, but just... exiting the cycle for good.",
